# Personal Portfolio Website

## Project Overview
This is my personal portfolio website developed to showcase my skills, projects, education, certifications, and contact information. The website is fully responsive and provides a professional overview of my work as an aspiring software developer.

## Features
- Responsive Design
- About Me Section
- Skills Section
- Projects Showcase
- Education Details
- Certifications
- Contact Information
- Social Media Links
- Smooth Navigation

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

